{"tid":1648804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌，咁撚多活動點去曬呀。","createTime":"2019-10-12T11:16:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T05:43:15.000Z","uid":258597,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"1739a87b1f495cc7ec6968f791c6e1ec2e558bba","tid":1648804,"uid":258597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:16:26.000Z","msg":"到左十月，大家開始想試新野，想十八區開花。呢樣野唔錯，但係你睇<br />\n<br />\n7月既日程表  <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n2vawiW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn2vawiW.jpg&h=94460838&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n10月既日程表<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NRa9MSe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNRa9MSe.jpg&h=ee0a9e11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喂大佬，一日咁多活動你叫人點去曬先。多區開花唔係唔得，但可唔可以唔好<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">將主線既同支線既group埋一齊</span></strong></span>。即係大遊行個類需要好多人既主線可以早幾日宣傳定。而有支線任想做既咪分開另一張表出，唔係個個市民都識得分邊個活動係重要邊個唔重要架。我都明白呢個月來發生太多大獲野，都應該可以成為主線。但係你<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1430係尖咀又一個感謝遊行，1500又一個緊急法遊行。</span></strong></span>你叫人半個鐘行曬再去下場？<br />\n<br />\n再者，要叫人都需要時間掛，你個update時間竟然係10/11，即係一日前。點spread呀大佬，人地收到張水蛇春咁長既list，揀去邊個都要時間啦。<br />\n<br />\n總結一下<br />\n<br />\n1）主線同支線日程<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">分開</span></span></strong></strong></span>出<br />\n<br />\n2）<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>3－4日前整好張主線日程</strong></span></span>，之後唔好大改。<br />\n<br />\n3）可以<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">整張日常任務</span></strong></span>，例如光顧黃店呀，鳩叫活動呀。呢張可以長期spread比全港人睇<br />\n<br />\n4）限制主線既數目，可能一日兩個已經最盡，真係好多既咪分開星期六1個星期日1個囉，香港人唔會介意行兩日。<br />\n<br />\n5）<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>咪撚撞活動呀</strong></span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n6）勇武既活動可以考慮其他方法宣傳，因為曝左光比狗知道人地可以預早佈署，對你地不利。但我相信都會影響到前數人數，唔建議立即做。<br />\n<br />\n運動到左樽頸位，大家唔好放棄。<br />\n堅持到底，就是勝利。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"ab00a556573aae3ad0d5887acd0d6fe38267c1e5","tid":1648804,"uid":258597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:16:45.000Z","msg":"自推10野"},{"pid":"285155d52a69d8fe360ec6a3b5b13dd7be889381","tid":1648804,"uid":258597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:17:01.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"ccb73ed9bb75fb0092b3a318d02f6c06d2046e75","tid":1648804,"uid":258597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:17:11.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"678039b88f44cb251be6d2b33a3c7621f4366bef","tid":1648804,"uid":93248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:17:18.000Z","msg":"推動BLIZZCON國際戰線要錢要人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1647163/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1647163/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"58497e449513ca316babb5f0ffd45f6783e85f7b","tid":1648804,"uid":258597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:17:23.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"56e1ea4f86b414a0aec2198a7b0ba49077dd4785","tid":1648804,"uid":258597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:17:33.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"ad03f7da22bcaa27dd79f9e2343480ed2ce31607","tid":1648804,"uid":258597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:17:50.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"b838539a6489136e59f19c1108cf05044dad521b","tid":1648804,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:18:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd584e8fcf075992ca6bc62d4337a73cea59ff00","tid":1648804,"uid":258597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:18:19.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"c68972e69e43d583a5554f753f5661fc3427a02e","tid":1648804,"uid":258597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite