rity <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ff577195e195cc540679128a9b6305f857ba7b","tid":1648804,"uid":258597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ea3ba8ffb31370e84405aa1b9085ff29ea92088","tid":1648804,"uid":265917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:31:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>小妹發現facebook好少文宣流通 <br />\n我自己一個帶風向帶到好絕望</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要記住尼場革命唔係淨係屬於連登仔<br />\n<br />\n四五十歲既人多數淨係上fb 佢地多數只會認同大眾都吹奏緊既野<br />\n<br />\n而藍屍page係fb大行其道<br />\n正所謂「識睇一定睇comment」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>所以我地要多啲係唔同post下面貼文宣同出下風向post </strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔該大家唔好淨係focus係twitter戰線 <br />\nFB戰線一樣咁撚重要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:38:06.000Z","msg":"其實係，連登都只係一個平台主要比年輕人組織活動，對於其他年齡層既人真係顧唔到太多。所以呢邊更加要做好，將好既文宣由呢到spread出去，再比用FB既中老年人睇到。咁樣先更有效，呢個建議其中都係為左要方便佢地睇而諗。"},{"pid":"5c72b85b83b7c561fb573f081330b48de0fbc8a2","tid":1648804,"uid":258597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79435bc47e5bd3d59f5cc35778710bf4fb53aa06","tid":1648804,"uid":264384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:33:53.000Z","msg":"想參加主線任 支線都會想參加但係要分priority <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:38:48.000Z","msg":"主線最好去得就去啦，始終媒體關注既係主線任比較多。"},{"pid":"727e2d9806da77e02ac9002a0d9f93770a2e89d2","tid":1648804,"uid":258597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:38:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce01aaa86fabcc8e0a431955ab27ad11dd33507c","tid":1648804,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"438cf9c6938b81b0e2c57c27063f1cb1658db2a5","tid":1648804,"uid":258597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eeb7f629381aa74023185664b3ab59c3393aa53a","tid":1648804,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,